    "Wang, Z., Zhang, F., Zheng, C., Hu, X., Cai, M., & Yang, C. (2024).",
    "MFAI: A Scalable Bayesian Matrix Factorization Approach to Leveraging Auxiliary Information.",
    "Journal of Computational and Graphical Statistics, 33(4), 1339â€“1349."
  ),
)

